SELECT  p.ProductionDetailId ,
            ISNULL(ProdQty,0)ProdQty ,
            pri.MaterialID ,
            p.Material MaterialName ,
            SUM(ISNULL(FactAmt, 0)) FactAmt ,
            ISNULL(AvgUPrice, 0) AvgUPrice,
			CASE WHEN ISNULL(CashPrice,0)=0 THEN ISNULL(pri.AvgUPrice,0) ELSE ISNULL(CashPrice,0) END AvgCashPrice
    INTO    #TempProduct
    FROM   [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.View_GetProductionFactAmt p WITH ( NOLOCK )
            LEFT JOIN Stations s WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON p.SiteId = s.StationID_ProductionSys
            OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 m.CSEMtrID FROM  dbo.MaterialMappingHistory m WITH ( NOLOCK ) where ISNULL(p.Material,'') = ISNULL(m.RecipeMtrName,'')
                                                           AND s.ID = m.StationID
                                                           AND m.isDeleted = 0
														   AND p.SiteProdTime >= m.EffectiveTime
														   ORDER BY m.ID DESC)m
            LEFT JOIN MaterialUPrice pri WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON m.CSEMtrID = pri.MaterialID
                                                            AND s.ID = pri.StationID
                                                            AND pri.PeriodID = @PeriodID
    WHERE   p.ProductionDetailId IN ( SELECT    OriginalID
                                      FROM      #TempDetails )
    GROUP BY p.ProductionDetailId ,
            ProdQty ,
            pri.MaterialID ,
            p.Material ,
            AvgUPrice,pri.CashPrice;

SELECT ID = detail.ID,                                    --日报明细ID
		   ProjectType=SalesPaymentType.Type,
		   AccountingPaymentType=ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, ''),
		--这里主要是为了区分  每一条明细使用的价格类型是什么  核算账户价格、代理商价格、现金销售政策价格
		  CalcType = CASE  
					 WHEN @BusinessType='SalesPriceCalculatePrice' THEN 
							CASE WHEN ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') != '现金' AND AutoPricingSet.SettlementPriceMode != 2 THEN 1
								 WHEN  ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') = '现金' OR ( ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') IN ('抵款','站点抵款') AND AutoPricingSet.SettlementPriceMode = 2 ) THEN 3 
							END
		             WHEN @BusinessType='AgentPriceCalculatePrice'AND ISNULL(AgentPriceDiff,0)=1 AND ISNULL(SalesDepartments.IsStationDepartment,0)=0 THEN 2 END,
					 --计算类型，销售日报自动挂价只区分合同价格和现金价格，给所有数据的合同金额字段、代理商金额字段挂价；代理商销售日报挂价，给有价差的代理商数据的代理商金额字段挂价
		   StationID = Report.StationID,
		   ProjectID = detail.ProjectID,                      --核算账户ID
		   AgentID = Project.AgentID,
		   ProductCategory = Project.ProductCategory,
		   IsBulkAndBagsSeparatePricing,                      --干混砂浆袋装混装是否单独计价
		   AutoPricingSet.CashUQtyAddPrice,
		   Unit = pc.Unit,
		   PlanId = MES.PlanId,                               --生产计划
		   ReportID = Report.ID,
		   ReportDate = Report.ReportDate,                    --报表日期
		   PeriodID = Periods.ID,                             --账期ID
		   SalesUnitWeigh = Project.SalesUnitWeigh,
		   StrengthGrade = detail.StrengthGrade,              --标准标号
		   Grade1 = detail.Grade1,                            --纯标号
		   Feature = detail.Feature,                          --性能拼接字段
		   FinalQty_T = detail.FinalQty_T,                    --销售吨量
		   FinalQty_M3 = detail.FinalQty_M3,                  --销售方量
		   Discharge = detail.Discharge,                      --卸料方式,
		   IsLubricatePumpMortar = MES.IsLubricatePumpMortar, --是否润泵砂浆
		   OriginalPlanGrade1 = MES.OriginalPlanGrade1,       --润泵砂浆关联原计划标号
		   OriginalPlanFeature = MES.OriginalPlanFeature,     --润泵砂浆关联原计划特殊要求
		   Overtime,                                          --超时时长
		   Distance = detail.Distance,                        --运距
		   VehicleNum = detail.VehicleSequence,
		   detail.IsProvidePump,--是否我方提供泵
		   detail.OtherPumpType--其他泵型
	INTO #TempData
	FROM ProductionDailyReportDetails detail WITH (NOLOCK)
		LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductionDailyReports Report WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.DailyReportID = Report.ID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.SalesDepartments WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.SalesDepartment = DepartmentName AND SalesDepartments.isDeleted = 0
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Project WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.ProjectID = Project.ID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductCategories pc WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.ProductCategory = pc.CategoryName
		LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.View_GetProductionDetailsAndLPM MES WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.OriginalID = MES.Id
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Periods WITH (NOLOCK) ON Report.ReportDate BETWEEN Periods.StartDate AND EndDate AND ISNULL(Periods.isDeleted, 0) = 0
		LEFT JOIN dbo.AutoPricingSet WITH (NOLOCK) ON BusinessType = 'Project' AND BusinessRelationID = detail.ProjectID AND AutoPricingSet.ProjectID = detail.ProjectID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.SalesPaymentType WITH(NOLOCK) ON Project.AccountingPaymentType=SalesPaymentType.PaymentType 
	WHERE ISNULL(Report.isDeleted, 0) = 0
		  AND detail.ProjectID IS NOT NULL
		  AND ISNULL(detail.IfManualUpdated, 0) = 0
		  AND Report.ReportDate
		  BETWEEN @StartDate AND @EndDate
		  AND ISNULL(detail.StrengthGrade, '') != ''
		  AND detail.TYPE IN (SELECT col FROM dbo.f_split((SELECT ParaValue FROM dbo.Parameters WHERE ParaName='ProjectSalesTypeFilter'),','))
		  AND ISNULL(SalesUPrice1,0)=0;

ISNULL(FinalQty_M3, 0) ELSE&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;   (CASE WHEN ISNULL(PriceSet.SettlementUnit, CalcData.Unit) = '吨' OR CalcData.CalcType = 3 THEN ISNULL(FinalQty_T, 0)&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;ELSE&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;(CASE WHEN ISNULL(CalcData.SalesUnitWeigh, 0) = 0 THEN 0 ELSE ISNULL(FinalQty_T, 0) / ISNULL(CalcData.SalesUnitWeigh, 0) END )&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;END)&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;   END,&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;  IsSpecialPrice=CASE WHEN CalcData.CalcType=3 THEN 0 ELSE ISNULL(PriceSet.IsSpecialPrice,1) END ,&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;  SpecialPriceScene=CASE WHEN CalcData.CalcType=3 THEN NULL ELSE  PriceSet.SpecialPriceScene END ,&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;  --具体使用的价格ID&#xD;&#xA;          PricingSetID=CASE WHEN CalcData.CalcType=3 THEN CashPriceSet.ID ELSE PriceSet.ID END &#xD;&#xA;&#x9;INTO #TempDataUsePrice&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;FROM (&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;       --区分具体的价格设置类型&#xD;&#xA;    SELECT BusinessType = CASE &#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;      WHEN CalcType = 1 THEN (CASE WHEN PriceAdj.ID IS NOT NULL THEN 'ProjectAdj' ELSE 'Project' END )&#xD;&#xA;                           WHEN CalcType = 2 THEN (CASE WHEN PriceAdj.ID IS NOT NULL THEN 'AgentPriceAdj' ELSE 'AgentPrice' END )&#xD;&#xA;                           WHEN CalcType = 3 THEN 'CashSalesPolicy'&#xD;&#xA;                       END,&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;   --区分具体的价格设置类型的ID&#xD;&#xA;           BusinessRelationID = CASE&#xD;&#xA;                            WHEN CalcType IN (1,2) THEN ISNULL(PriceAdj.ID,#TempData.ProjectID)&#xD;&#xA;                            WHEN CalcType = 3 THEN CashSalesPolicySet.ID&#xD;&#xA;                        END,&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;--区分具体的适用品类&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;ApplicableStrengthGrade=CASE WHEN  ProductCategory='干混砂浆' AND IsBulkAndBagsSeparatePricing=1 &#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9; THEN&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;                                   CASE WHEN StrengthGrade LIKE '%袋装%' THEN 'DryMixMortarBulkInBags' ELSE 'DryMixMortarBulk' END&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;ELSE 'ALL' END,&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;#TempData.*&#xD;&#xA;    FROM #TempData&#xD;&#xA;        LEFT JOIN dbo.Stations WITH (NOLOCK) ON #TempData.StationID = Stations.ID&#xD;&#xA;        OUTER APPLY&#xD;&#xA;    (&#xD;&#xA;        SELECT TOP 1&#xD;&#xA;               Adj.ID&#xD;&#xA;        FROM AutoPricingAdj Adj WITH (NOLOCK)&#xD;&#xA;        WHERE Adj.IsDeleted = 0&#xD;&#xA;              AND CASE WHEN Adj.BusinessType='ProjectAdj' THEN 1 ELSE 2 END = #TempData.CalcType --合同计价模式&#xD;&#xA;              AND Adj.ProjectID = #TempData.ProjectID&#xD;&#xA;              AND #TempData.ReportDate&#xD;&#xA;              BETWEEN Adj.EffectTime AND ISNULL(Adj.ExpireTime, GETDATE())&#xD;&#xA;        ORDER BY EffectTime DESC&#xD;&#xA;    ) PriceAdj&#xD;&#xA;        --查询此事业部，符合时间范围的销售政策&#xD;&#xA;        OUTER APPLY&#xD;&#xA;    (&#xD;&#xA;        SELECT TOP 1&#xD;&#xA;               ID&#xD;&#xA;        FROM CashSalesPolicySet WITH (NOLOCK)&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#xD;&#xA;        WHERE IsDeleted = 0&#xD;&#xA;              AND RegionID = Stations.RegionID&#xD;&#xA;              AND #TempData.ReportDate&#xD;&#xA;              BETWEEN CashSalesPolicySet.EffectTime AND ISNULL(dbo.CashSalesPolicySet.ExpireTime, GETDATE())&#xD;&#xA;        ORDER BY EffectTime DESC&#xD;&#xA;    ) CashSalesPolicySet&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;)CalcData&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;--匹配价格设置的使用品类标号&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;LEFT JOIN dbo.AutoPricingSet PriceSet WITH(NOLOCK) ON PriceSet.BusinessType = CalcData.BusinessType AND PriceSet.BusinessRelationID = CalcData.BusinessRelationID AND PriceSet.ApplicableStrengthGrade = CalcData.ApplicableStrengthGrade&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;--匹配此销售政策下的品类&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;LEFT JOIN CashSalesPolicyCategorySet CashPriceSet WITH (NOLOCK) ON CalcData.CalcType=3 AND CashPriceSet.CashSalesPolicySetID= CalcData.BusinessRelationID AND CashPriceSet.ProductCategory = CalcData.ProductCategory&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;--==================================================Step3：更新日报的是否特殊定价，并从需要计算价格的数据中移除==================================================--&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#xD;&#xA;" StatementText="&#x9;SELECT  CalcData.ID ,--日报明细ID&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;Discharge,&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;CashUQtyAddPrice=ISNULL((SELECT CashUQtyAddPrice FROM dbo.AutoPricingSet WHERE ProjectID=CalcData.ProjectID AND BusinessType='Project'),0),--每单位加收&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;SettlementUnit=CalcData.Unit,--结算单位 为空的话取核算账户品类对应的单位&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;DecimalsRetainMode='Round',--小数位保留方式,RoundDown抹零,Round四舍五入&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;DecimalsRetainDigit=2,--小数位保留位数 0 1 2&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;CalculateFinalQty=CASE WHEN CalcData.Unit='方' THEN ISNULL(FinalQty_M3,0) ELSE  ISNULL(FinalQty_T,0) END,--计算量&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;CashSalesPolicyCategorySetID=CashSalesPolicyCategorySet.ID,--品类ID&#xD;&#xA;                AdjGradeID = CashSalesPolicyPriceGradeDetails.ID ,--特殊标号固定价数据id&#xD;&#xA;                AdjGradePrice = ISNULL(CashSalesPolicyPriceGradeDetails.UnInvoicedPrice, 0) ,--特殊标号固定价格&#xD;&#xA;                AdjFeaturePrice = ISNULL(AdjFeaturePrices.AdjFeaturePrice, 0),--特殊性能固定价格汇总&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;SelfWithdrawalAmt=ISNULL(CashSalesPolicyPriceGradeDetails.SelfWithdrawalAmt, 0)--自提减现金额&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;INTO #TempCashPrice&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;FROM #TempDataUsePrice CalcData&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;--匹配此销售政策下的品类&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;INNER JOIN CashSalesPolicyCategorySet WITH (NOLOCK) ON CashSalesPolicyCategorySet.ID = CalcData.PricingSetID&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;--查询此品类下适用全部站点的单价策略&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;LEFT JOIN dbo.CashSalesPolicyPriceSet AllPriceSet WITH (NOLOCK) ON AllPriceSet.CashSalesPolicyCategorySetID = CashSalesPolicyCategorySet.ID AND AllPriceSet.Remark = '全部'&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;LEFT JOIN (&#x9;SELECT CashSalesPolicyCategorySetID,CashSalesPolicyPriceSetID,StationID &#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;FROM  CashSalesPolicyPriceSet PriceSet WITH (NOLOCK) &#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;--查询此品类下对应站点的单价策略&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;LEFT JOIN dbo.CashSalesPolicyPriceStationsDetails WITH (NOLOCK) ON CashSalesPolicyPriceStationsDetails.CashSalesPolicyPriceSetID = PriceSet.ID &#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;WHERE PriceSet.Remark != '全部'&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;)CashSalesPolicyPriceStationsDetails ON CashSalesPolicyCategorySet.ID=CashSalesPolicyPriceStationsDetails.CashSalesPolicyCategorySetID AND CashSalesPolicyPriceStationsDetails.StationID=CalcData.StationID&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;--查询此品类下对应站点的单价策略的标号价格设置&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;LEFT JOIN dbo.CashSalesPolicyPriceGradeDetails WITH (NOLOCK) ON CashSalesPolicyPriceGradeDetails.CashSalesPolicyPriceSetID = (CASE WHEN AllPriceSet.ID IS NOT NULL THEN AllPriceSet.ID ELSE CashSalesPolicyPriceStationsDetails.CashSalesPolicyPriceSetID END) AND Grade = CalcData.Grade1&#xD;&#xA;            --关联特殊定价性能表取性能汇总固定金额&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;OUTER APPLY ( SELECT    SUM(ISNULL(FeatureDetails.Price, 0)) AdjFeaturePrice&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;FROM      dbo.f_split1(CalcData.Feature, ',') A&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;LEFT JOIN CashSalesPolicyFeaturePrices FeatureDetails&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON A.name = FeatureDetails.Feature&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;WHERE     FeatureDetails.CashSalesPolicyCategorySetID = CashSalesPolicyCategorySet.ID&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;AND ISNULL(name, '') != ''&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;) AdjFeaturePrices&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;WHERE CalcType=3&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    --==================================================Step3：计算价格 UPDATE ins
	SET ReceivingDailyReportID = NULL
	FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
	WHERE ins.TenantId = @TenantID AND ins.SiteDate>= DATEADD(MONTH, -2, CAST(@ReportDate AS DATE))
		  AND NOT EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
			left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
				ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	);

UPDATE ins
	   SET ReceivingDailyReportID = r.ID
	   FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		   left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		   left JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON ins.TenantId = r.TenantID
				  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	   WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			 AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
			 AND r.ID = ISNULL(@ReportID, r.ID);

UPDATE ins
	   SET ReceivingDailyReportID = r.ID
	   FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		   left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		   left JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON ins.TenantId = r.TenantID
				  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	   WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			 AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
			 AND r.ID = ISNULL(@ReportID, r.ID);

UPDATE ins
	SET ReceivingDailyReportID = NULL
	FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
	WHERE ins.TenantId = @TenantID AND ins.SiteDate>= DATEADD(MONTH, -2, CAST(@ReportDate AS DATE))
		  AND NOT EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
			left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
				ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	);

UPDATE ins
	SET ReceivingDailyReportID = NULL
	FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
	WHERE ins.TenantId = @TenantID AND ins.SiteDate>= DATEADD(MONTH, -2, CAST(@ReportDate AS DATE))
		  AND NOT EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
			left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
				ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	);

UPDATE ins
	SET ReceivingDailyReportID = NULL
	FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
	WHERE ins.TenantId = @TenantID AND ins.SiteDate>= DATEADD(MONTH, -2, CAST(@ReportDate AS DATE))
		  AND NOT EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
			left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
				ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	);

UPDATE ins
	SET ReceivingDailyReportID = NULL
	FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
	WHERE ins.TenantId = @TenantID AND ins.SiteDate>= DATEADD(MONTH, -2, CAST(@ReportDate AS DATE))
		  AND NOT EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
			left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
				ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	);

UPDATE ins
	   SET ReceivingDailyReportID = r.ID
	   FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		   left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		   left JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON ins.TenantId = r.TenantID
				  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	   WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			 AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
			 AND r.ID = ISNULL(@ReportID, r.ID);

UPDATE ins
	SET ReceivingDailyReportID = NULL
	FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
	WHERE ins.TenantId = @TenantID AND ins.SiteDate>= DATEADD(MONTH, -2, CAST(@ReportDate AS DATE))
		  AND NOT EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
			left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
				ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	);

UPDATE ins
	   SET ReceivingDailyReportID = r.ID
	   FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		   left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		   left JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON ins.TenantId = r.TenantID
				  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	   WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			 AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
			 AND r.ID = ISNULL(@ReportID, r.ID);

INSERT INTO dbo.ProductionDailyReportDetails
    (
        FGC_CreateDate,
        FGC_LastModifier,
        FGC_LastModifyDate,
        FGC_Creator,
        DailyReportID,
        Type,
        OriginalID,
        OriginalProjectID,
        OriginalPlanID,
        ProjectName,
        Customer,
        SalesDepartment,
        Salesman,
        PaymentType,
        ProductCategory,
        Unit,
        ConstructionPosition,
        StrengthGrade,
        Discharge,
        ReceiptDate,
        ProductionLine,
        ProductionTime,
        VehicleNum,
        VehicleSequence,
        Driver,
        PlanType,
        ApplicationUser,
        ProductionCoefficient,
        ProductionQty_M3,
        ProductionQty_T,
        ReceiptQty,
        SignedQty_M3,
        SignedQty_T,
        FinalQty_M3,
        FinalQty_T,
        TSFInQty,
        TSFOutQty,
        ActualSupplyQty_M3,
        ActualSupplyQty_T,
        SignCopy,
        Distance,
        Overtime,
        ProductionRemarks,
        LogisticsCoefficient,
        LogisticsFinalQty_M3,
        ProjectID,
        SalesCoefficient,
		SalesRemarks,
        LogisticsOvertime,
        SlumpTypes,
        VehicleRegNum,
        Grade1,
        Feature,
        IsProvidePump,
        IfManualUpdated,
        AcumltQuantity,
        SignedQtyDiffReasonType,
        Area,
        TechnologyRequest,
		StubCopy,
		ShipmentCount,
		Paid,
		ScaleDiff,
		LossQty,
		PrintTime,
		PrintOperatorID,
		PrintOperator,
		Metre,
		OtherPumpType,
		ProductionPlanNumber,
		PlatformCustomer,
		PlatformCustomerPhone,
		EGCBOrderID
    )
    SELECT
        FGC_CreateDate=GETDATE(),
        FGC_LastModifier=@Creator ,
        FGC_LastModifyDate=GETDATE() ,
        FGC_Creator=@Creator ,
        DailyReportID = r.ID,
        Type = ISNULL(ISNULL(mt.ProductionNature,Stations.Type),'自产'),
        OriginalID = mt.Id,
        OriginalProjectID = mt.ProjectId,
        OriginalPlanID = mt.PlanId,
        ProjectName = mt.ProjectName,
        Customer = mt.CompanyName,
        SalesDepartment =ISNULL(mt.Department, @DefaultDepartment),
        Salesman =  ISNULL(mt.PersonInCharge, '未填'),
        PaymentType = ISNULL(mt.PaymentType, @DefaultPaymentType),
        ProductCategory =ISNULL(mt.ConcreteCategory, @DefaultProductCategory) ,
		Unit = ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit),
		ConstructionPosition = mt.Position,
		StrengthGrade = mt.Grade,
		Discharge = mt.DischargeType,
		ReceiptDate = CAST(mt.Date AS DATE),
		ProductionLine = mt.TerminalNo,
		ProductionTime = mt.ProductionTime,
		VehicleNum = mt.VehicleNo,
		VehicleSequence=mt.VehicleNum,
		Driver = mt.DriverName,
		PlanType = mt.Type,
		ApplicationUser = mt.Creator,
		ProductionCoefficient = CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END,
		ProductionQty_M3 = CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN
										mt.ActQuantity / (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
								ELSE mt.ActQuantity END,--生产方量=如果单位=吨，就取【mt.ActQuantity/生产容重系数】，否则=【mt.ActQuantity】
		ProductionQty_T = CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN mt.ActQuantity ELSE NULL END,--生产吨量=如果单位=吨，就取【mt.ActQuantity】，否则=【null】
		ReceiptQty = mt.FaceQuantity,
		SignedQty_M3 = CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
								(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
							ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END) END,--签收方量=如果单位=吨，就取【实际签收量/容重】
		SignedQty_T=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
					(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
					ELSE NULL END,--签收吨量=如果单位=吨，就取【实际签收量】
		FinalQty_M3=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '方' THEN 
						(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
						ELSE NULL END,--销售方量=如果单位=方，就取【实际签收量】
		FinalQty_T=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
					(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
					ELSE NULL END,--销售吨量=如果单位=吨，就取【实际签收量】
		TSFInQty=mt.TransferIn,
		TSFOutQty=mt.TransferOut,
		ActualSupplyQty_M3=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
									(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN  (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN mt.ActQuantity ELSE NULL END)+mt.TransferIn-mt.TransferOut ELSE NULL END)
									/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
								ELSE 
									(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN mt.ActQuantity / (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END) ELSE mt.ActQuantity END)+mt.TransferIn-mt.TransferOut
								END,--实供方量=如果单位=吨，就取【实供吨量/生产容重系数】，否则=【生产方量+调入-调出】
		ActualSupplyQty_T=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
								(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN mt.ActQuantity ELSE NULL END)+mt.TransferIn-mt.TransferOut
							ELSE NULL END,--实供吨量=如果单位=吨，就取【生产吨量+调入-调出】
		SignCopy=mt.ReceiptSigned,
		Distance=CASE WHEN mt.DeliveryDistance>0 THEN mt.DeliveryDistance ELSE mt.HaulDistance END,--运距=如果签收运距>0 取【签收运距】，否则取【计划运距】
		Overtime = mt.Overtime,
		ProductionRemarks='更新日志：'+ISNULL(mt.UpdateLogs,'')+'；报表备注：'+ ISNULL(mt.Comment,'') +'；小票备注：'+ ISNULL(mt.PrintComment,''),--生产备注
		LogisticsCoefficient=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END,--物流容重系数=生产容重系数
		LogisticsFinalQty_M3=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
									(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
								ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END) END,--物流方量=签收方量
		ProjectID=mt.SourceId1,
		SalesCoefficient= CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END,--销售容重=生产容重系数
		SalesRemarks=mt.Remark,--销售备注
		LogisticsOvertime=mt.Overtime,
		SlumpTypes=mt.Slump,
		VehicleRegNum=mt.VehiclePlate,
		Grade1=mt.Grade1,
		Feature=CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.Feature,'')='' THEN NULL ELSE mt.Feature END,
		IsProvidePump=mt.IsProvidePump,
		0 IfManualUpdated,
		AcumltQuantity=mt.AcumltQuantity,
		SignedQtyDiffReasonType=mt.SignedQtyDiffReason,
		Area=mt.Region,
		TechnologyRequest=TechnologyRequest,
		StubCopy=1,
		ShipmentCount=1,
		Paid=0,
		ScaleDiff=CASE WHEN mt.SignedQtyDiffReason=2 THEN 
					mt.FaceQuantity-
					(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
							(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
							(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
							ELSE NULL END)
					 ELSE 
					        (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
								(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
							ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END) END)
					 END)
		          ELSE 
				    NULL
				  END,--磅差=如果SignedQtyDiffReasonType=2，则取【如果单位=吨，就用票面量-签收吨量，否则用票面量-签收方量】，否则=null
		LossQty=CASE WHEN mt.SignedQtyDiffReason IN (3,4,5) THEN 
		             mt.FaceQuantity-
					(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
							(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
							(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
							ELSE NULL END)
					 ELSE 
					        (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
								(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
							ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END) END)
					 END)
				ELSE 
				    NULL
				END,--损耗=如果签收方量差异在345 则（如果单位=吨  就用）
		mt.PrintTime,
		mt.PrintOperatorID,
		mt.PrintOperator,
		Metre=mt.Meters,
		OtherPumpType=mt.OtherPumpType,
		mt.Code,
		mt.EgcbOrderCreator,
		mt.EgcbOrderCreatorPhone,
		mt.EGCBOrderID
    FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.[ProductDetailsDino-mt] mt WITH (NOLOCK)
		--[172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.[ProductDetailsDino-mt] mt WITH (NOLOCK)
        INNER JOIN dbo.Stations WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON Stations.StationID_ProductionSys = mt.SiteId AND Stations.isDeleted=0
        INNER JOIN ProductionDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON r.StationID = Stations.ID
               AND r.isDeleted = 0
               AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
        LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductCategories pc WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON pc.CategoryName = ISNULL(mt.ConcreteCategory, @DefaultProductCategory)
    WHERE mt.TenantId=@TenantID AND
		  mt.SiteDate >= @ReportDate
          AND mt.SiteDate < DATEADD(DAY, 1, @ReportDate) --生成17号日报  获取>=17 0:00  <18 0:00的数据
	UNION
	SELECT FGC_CreateDate = GETDATE(),
		FGC_LastModifier = @Creator,
		FGC_LastModifyDate = GETDATE(),
		FGC_Creator =@Creator,
		DailyReportID = r.ID,
		Type = Stations.Type,
		OriginalID=RIGHT(Shipping.Number,12),
		OriginalProjectID,
		OriginalPlanID=NULL,
		ProjectName=Shipping.ProjectName,
		Customer=Shipping.Consignee,
		SalesDepartment=ISNULL(Project.SalesDepartment, @DefaultDepartment),
		Salesman=ISNULL(Project.Salesman,'未填'),
		PaymentType=ISNULL(Project.SalesPaymentType,@DefaultPaymentType),
		ProductCategory=ISNULL(up.ConcreteCategory,'干混砂浆'),
		Unit=@DefaultGHSJUnit,
		ConstructionPosition=Shipping.Position,
		StrengthGrade=ISNULL(Delivering.grade,Delivering.Item+'-'+Delivering.Specification),
		Discharge=NULL,
		ReceiptDate = CAST(Delivering.GrossTime AS DATE),
		ProductionLine=NULL,
		ProductionTime=Delivering.GrossTime,
		VehicleNum=Delivering.Vehicle,
		VehicleSequence=NULL,
		Driver=NULL,
		PlanType=up.Type,
		ApplicationUser=up.Creator,
		ProductionCoefficient=NULL,
		ProductionQty_M3=NULL,
		ProductionQty_T=Delivering.RealNet/1000,
		ReceiptQty=Delivering.Net/1000,
		SignedQty_M3=NULL,
		SignedQty_T=Delivering.Net/1000,
		FinalQty_M3=NULL,
		FinalQty_T=Delivering.Net/1000,
		TSFInQty=NULL,
		TSFOutQty=NULL,
		ActualSupplyQty_M3=NULL,
		ActualSupplyQty_T=Delivering.Net/1000,
		SignCopy=NULL,
		Distance=p.HaulDistance,
		Overtime=NULL,
		ProductionRemarks=NULL,
		LogisticsCoefficient=NULL,
		LogisticsFinalQty_M3=NULL,
		ProjectID=Shipping.ProjectID,
		SalesCoefficient=NULL,
		SalesRemarks=NULL,
		LogisticsOvertime=NULL,
		SlumpTypes=NULL,
		VehicleRegNum=NULL,
		grade1=Delivering.grade1,
		feature=CASE WHEN ISNULL(Delivering.feature,'')='' THEN NULL ELSE Delivering.feature END,
		IsProvidePump=NULL,
		IfManualUpdated=0,
		AcumltQuantity=NULL,
		SignedQtyDiffReasonType=NULL,
		Area=NULL,
		TechnologyRequest=NULL,
		StubCopy=1,
		ShipmentCount=NULL,
		Paid=0,
		ScaleDiff=NULL,
		LossQty=NULL,
		PrintTime=NULL,
		PrintOperatorID=NULL,
		PrintOperator=NULL,
		Metre=NULL,
		OtherPumpType=NULL,
		p.Code,
		up.EgcbOrderCreator,
	    up.EgcbOrderCreatorPhone,
		up.EGCBOrderID
	FROM 
	[Weighbridge].dbo.Shipping Shipping WITH (NOLOCK)
	LEFT JOIN [Weighbridge].dbo.Delivering Delivering WITH (NOLOCK)
		ON Shipping.DeliveringID = Delivering.ID
	LEFT JOIN  [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.UserPlans up WITH(NOLOCK) ON Delivering.UserPlanID=up.id
	LEFT JOIN  [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.Plans p WITH(NOLOCK) ON up.PlanId=p.id
	--[Weighbridge].dbo.Shipping Shipping WITH (NOLOCK)
	--LEFT JOIN [Weighbridge].dbo.Delivering Delivering WITH (NOLOCK)
	--	ON Shipping.DeliveringID = Delivering.ID
	LEFT JOIN dbo.Project WITH(NOLOCK) ON Shipping.ProjectID=Project.ID
	INNER JOIN dbo.Stations WITH (NOLOCK)
		ON Stations.StationID_WeighbridgeSys = Shipping.StationID
			AND Stations.isDeleted = 0
	INNER JOIN ProductionDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		ON r.StationID = Stations.ID
			AND r.isDeleted = 0
			AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
	WHERE Shipping.isDeleted = 0
		AND Delivering.GrossTime >=DATEADD(HOUR,@DefaultFinancialTime,@ReportDate)
		AND Delivering.GrossTime < DATEADD(DAY, 1, DATEADD(HOUR,@DefaultFinancialTime,@ReportDate)) --生成17号日报  获取>=17 0:00  <18 0:00的数据
		AND Shipping.isDeleted=0 AND Delivering.isDeleted=0

								detail.Feature ,--性能拼接字段
                                0 CalculatePrice , --自动挂价计算后的价格  如果没有  默认0
                                detail.Overtime ,--超时时长
                                0 SalesOvertimeAmt ,--超时费
                                0 SalesReorderLogisticsAmt ,--补方物流费
                                detail.FinalQty_T ,--销售吨量
                                detail.FinalQty_M3 ,--销售方量
                                0 SalesPumpAmt ,--泵送费
                                ProductionDetails.VehicleNum ,--车次
                                0 GuidePrice ,--信息价
                                0 FeaturePrice ,--特殊单价
                                0 FloatRate,--浮动比例
								'' SpecialPriceScene, --特殊定价场景
								NULL IsSpecialPrice --是否特殊定价
                        FROM    ProductionDailyReportDetails detail WITH ( NOLOCK )
                                LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductionDailyReports Report
                                WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON detail.DailyReportID = Report.ID
                                LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.ProductionDetails
                                WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON detail.OriginalID = ProductionDetails.Id
                                LEFT JOIN dbo.Periods WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON Report.ReportDate BETWEEN Periods.StartDate
                                                              AND
                                                              EndDate
                                                              AND ISNULL(Periods.isDeleted,
                                                              0) = 0
                        WHERE   ISNULL(Report.isDeleted, 0) = 0
								AND detail.ProjectID IS NOT NULL
                                AND DATEDIFF(DAY,Report.ReportDate,CONVERT(VARCHAR(10),GETDATE(),120))<=3 
                                AND ISNULL(detail.StrengthGrade, '') != ''
								AND detail.PaymentType IN ('垫资','月结100%','预付款')
								AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM dbo.Project WITH(NOLOCK)  WHERE AccountingPaymentType='现金' AND ID=detail.ProjectID)
								AND detail.Type IN (SELECT col FROM dbo.f_split((SELECT ParaValue FROM dbo.Parameters WHERE ParaName='ProjectSalesTypeFilter'),','));

0)  ,--结算税率&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;SettlementUnit=ISNULL(PriceAdj.SettlementUnit,pc.Unit),--结算单位 为空的话取核算账户品类对应的单位&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;DecimalsRetainMode=ISNULL(PriceAdj.DecimalsRetainMode,'Round'),--小数位保留方式,RoundDown抹零,Round四舍五入&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;DecimalsRetainDigit=ISNULL(PriceAdj.DecimalsRetainDigit,2),--小数位保留位数 0 1 2&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;CalculateFinalQty=CASE WHEN pc.Unit='方' THEN ISNULL(FinalQty_M3,0) ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(PriceAdj.SettlementUnit,pc.Unit)='吨' THEN ISNULL(FinalQty_T,0)else (CASE WHEN ISNULL(p.SalesUnitWeigh,0)=0 THEN 0 ELSE ISNULL(FinalQty_T,0)/ISNULL(p.SalesUnitWeigh,0) END) end) end,--计算量&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;                PriceAdj.SettlementPriceMode ,--结算价模式  0：固定价;1：信息价&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.ReferenceGuidePriceCity ,--参考信息价城市&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.ReferenceGuidePriceType ,--参考信息价类型(1：上月；2：本月；3：上上月)&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.SettlementMode,--结算方式（0：本月；1：跨月）&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.SettlementDate,--结算时间（每月）&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.PriceCalculationMode ,--浮动比率&#xD;&#xA;                FixedUPrice=ISNULL(PriceAdj.FixedUPrice, 0)  ,--固定价金额&#xD;&#xA;                GuidePrice = CASE WHEN gp.id IS NULL AND PriceAdj.ReferenceGuidePriceType = 2 THEN CASE WHEN PriceAdj.PriceCalculationMode = 1 THEN ISNULL(LastGp.InclTaxPrice, 0) ELSE ISNULL(LastGp.NonTaxPrice, 0) END ELSE CASE WHEN PriceAdj.PriceCalculationMode = 1 THEN ISNULL(gp.InclTaxPrice, 0) ELSE ISNULL(gp.NonTaxPrice, 0) END END,--信息价（含税/不含税）&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;ReferencePrices.ID ReferencePricesID,--参考标号ID&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;ReferencePrices.Price ,--特殊标号固定价数据id&#xD;&#xA;                AdjGradePrice = ISNULL(AdjGradeDetails.Price, 0) ,--特殊标号固定价格&#xD;&#xA;                AdjFeaturePrice = ISNULL(AdjFeaturePrices.AdjFeaturePrice, 0),--特殊性能固定价格汇总&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;OverTimePricingMode=ISNULL(PriceAdj.OverTimePricingMode,0),--超时费计价模式&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;OverTimeUPrice=ISNULL(PriceAdj.OverTimeUPrice,0),--超时单价&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;UnOneHourOverTimeUPrice=ISNULL(PriceAdj.UnOneHourOverTimeUPrice,0),--超时单价（不足一小时）&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.InsufficientQtyAddType,--不足方量加收类型（1：按次加收；0：按方量加收）&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.SingleMinQty,--单次最小方量&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.UQtyAddPrice,--每方加收&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.IsUPriceIncludedPump,--单价是否含泵（0：否；1：是）&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;PriceAdj.PumpPrice--非泵送减/泵送单价（含税）&#xD;&#xA; StatementText=" SELECT  #TempData.ID ,--日报明细ID&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;p.AgentID,--代理商ID&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;    p.IsSpecialPrice,--是否特殊定价（0：否；1：是）&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;p.SpecialPriceScene,--特殊定价场景&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;    SettlementTaxRate=ISNULL(p.SettlementTaxRate, 0)  ,--结算税率&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;SettlementUnit=  ISNULL(p.SettlementUnit,pc.Unit),--结算单位 为空的话取核算账户品类对应的单位&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;DecimalsRetainMode=ISNULL(p.DecimalsRetainMode,'Round'),--小数位保留方式,RoundDown抹零,Round四舍五入&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;DecimalsRetainDigit=ISNULL(p.DecimalsRetainDigit,2),--小数位保留位数 0 1 2&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;CalculateFinalQty=CASE WHEN pc.Unit='方' THEN ISNULL(FinalQty_M3,0) ELSE (CASE WHEN  ISNULL(p.SettlementUnit,pc.Unit)='吨' THEN ISNULL(FinalQty_T,0)else SELECT ID = detail.ID,                                    --日报明细ID
		   ProjectType=SalesPaymentType.Type,
		   AccountingPaymentType=ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, ''),
		--这里主要是为了区分  每一条明细使用的价格类型是什么  核算账户价格、代理商价格、现金销售政策价格
		  CalcType = CASE  
					 WHEN @BusinessType='SalesPriceCalculatePrice' THEN 
							CASE WHEN ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') != '现金' AND AutoPricingSet.SettlementPriceMode != 2 THEN 1
								 WHEN  ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') = '现金' OR ( ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') in ('抵款','站点抵款') AND AutoPricingSet.SettlementPriceMode = 2 ) THEN 3 
							END
		             WHEN @BusinessType='AgentPriceCalculatePrice'AND ISNULL(AgentPriceDiff,0)=1 AND ISNULL(SalesDepartments.IsStationDepartment,0)=0 THEN 2 END,
					 --计算类型，销售日报自动挂价只区分合同价格和现金价格，给所有数据的合同金额字段、代理商金额字段挂价；代理商销售日报挂价，给有价差的代理商数据的代理商金额字段挂价
		   StationID = Report.StationID,
		   ProjectID = detail.ProjectID,                      --核算账户ID
		   AgentID = Project.AgentID,
		   ProductCategory = Project.ProductCategory,
		   IsBulkAndBagsSeparatePricing,                      --干混砂浆袋装混装是否单独计价
		   AutoPricingSet.CashUQtyAddPrice,
		   Unit = pc.Unit,
		   PlanId = MES.PlanId,                               --生产计划
		   ReportID = Report.ID,
		   ReportDate = Report.ReportDate,                    --报表日期
		   PeriodID = Periods.ID,                             --账期ID
		   SalesUnitWeigh = Project.SalesUnitWeigh,
		   StrengthGrade = detail.StrengthGrade,              --标准标号
		   Grade1 = detail.Grade1,                            --纯标号
		   Feature = detail.Feature,                          --性能拼接字段
		   FinalQty_T = detail.FinalQty_T,                    --销售吨量
		   FinalQty_M3 = detail.FinalQty_M3,                  --销售方量
		   Discharge = detail.Discharge,                      --卸料方式,
		   IsLubricatePumpMortar = MES.IsLubricatePumpMortar, --是否润泵砂浆
		   OriginalPlanGrade1 = MES.OriginalPlanGrade1,       --润泵砂浆关联原计划标号
		   OriginalPlanFeature = MES.OriginalPlanFeature,     --润泵砂浆关联原计划特殊要求
		   Overtime,                                          --超时时长
		   Distance = detail.Distance,                        --运距
		   VehicleNum = detail.VehicleSequence,
		   detail.IsProvidePump,--是否我方提供泵
		   detail.OtherPumpType,--其他泵型
		   detail.Metre
		   --oup.OrderID
	INTO #TempData
	FROM ProductionDailyReportDetails detail WITH (NOLOCK)
		LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductionDailyReports Report WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.DailyReportID = Report.ID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.SalesDepartments WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.SalesDepartment = DepartmentName AND SalesDepartments.isDeleted = 0
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Project WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.ProjectID = Project.ID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductCategories pc WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.ProductCategory = pc.CategoryName
		LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.View_GetProductionDetailsAndLPM MES WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.OriginalID = MES.Id
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Periods WITH (NOLOCK) ON Report.ReportDate BETWEEN Periods.StartDate AND EndDate AND ISNULL(Periods.isDeleted, 0) = 0
		LEFT JOIN dbo.AutoPricingSet WITH (NOLOCK) ON BusinessType = 'Project' AND BusinessRelationID = detail.ProjectID AND AutoPricingSet.ProjectID = detail.ProjectID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.SalesPaymentType WITH(NOLOCK) ON Project.AccountingPaymentType=SalesPaymentType.PaymentType 
		--交易平台自动挂价
		--LEFT JOIN [e-GCB].dbo.OrderUserPlans oup WITH(NOLOCK) ON MES.UserPlanID=oup.MesUserPlanID AND oup.IsDeleted=0
	WHERE ISNULL(Report.isDeleted, 0) = 0
		  AND detail.ProjectID IS NOT NULL
		  AND ISNULL(detail.IfManualUpdated, 0) = 0
		  AND detail.SalesDepartment IN
			  (
				  SELECT col FROM dbo.f_split(@SalesDepartments, ',')
			  )
		  AND Report.ReportDate
		  BETWEEN @StartDate AND @EndDate
		  AND ISNULL(detail.StrengthGrade, '') != ''
		  AND detail.Type IN (SELECT col FROM dbo.f_split((SELECT ParaValue FROM dbo.Parameters WHERE ParaName='ProjectSalesTypeFilter'),','))
		  AND detail.EGCBOrderID IS NULL
		  --AND oup.OrderID IS NULL;

SELECT pd.Date,
           Project.ID,
           Number,
           ProjectName,
           CompanyName_PartyA,
           CashAccounts.Salesman,
           SalesDepartment,
           ProductCategory,
           Plans.Id PlanID,
           pd.VehicleNo,
           pd.VehicleNum,
           Plans.Grade1,
           Plans.Feature,
           Plans.Quantity PlanQuantity,
           pd.FaceQuantity,
           ActQuantity,
           pd.SignedQuantity,
           pd.HaulDistance,
           CashAccountUsedDetails.UsedAmount
    INTO #TempDetails
    FROM dbo.CashAccounts WITH (NOLOCK)
        LEFT JOIN dbo.CashAccountProjects WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON CashAccountID = CashAccounts.ID
               AND CashAccountProjects.IsDeleted = 0
        LEFT JOIN dbo.Project WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON CashAccountProjects.ProjectID = Project.ID
        LEFT JOIN dbo.CashAccountUsedDetails WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON CashAccountUsedDetails.ProjectID = CashAccountProjects.ProjectID
               AND CashAccountUsedDetails.IsDeleted = 0
               AND BusinessType IN ( 0, 1 )
        LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.ProductionDetails pd WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON MesProductionDetailID = pd.Id
        LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.Plans Plans WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON pd.PlanId = Plans.Id
    WHERE CashAccounts.IsDeleted = 0
          AND CashAccounts.Salesman = ISNULL(@Salesman, CashAccounts.Salesman)
          AND
          (
              CompanyName_PartyA LIKE '%' + ISNULL(@CompanyName, '') + '%'
              OR ProjectName LIKE '%' + ISNULL(@ProjectName, '') + '%'
          )
          AND ProductCategory = ISNULL(@ProductCategory, ProductCategory)
          AND Plans.Grade1 = ISNULL(@Grade, Plans.Grade1)
    AND pd.Date
    BETWEEN ISNULL(@StartDate, pd.Date) AND ISNULL(@EndData, GETDATE());

ON|OFF&#xD;&#xA;--GO&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;/*获取现金账户实时账单列表*/&#xD;&#xA;CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[usp_GetCashAccountProjectBillList]&#xD;&#xA;    @Salesman AS NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,&#xD;&#xA;    @ProjectName AS NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,&#xD;&#xA;    @CompanyName AS NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,&#xD;&#xA;    @ProductCategory AS NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,&#xD;&#xA;    @Grade AS NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,&#xD;&#xA;    @StartDate AS DATETIME = NULL,&#xD;&#xA;    @EndData AS DATETIME = NULL,&#xD;&#xA;    @PageSize INT = 20, --每页行数&#xD;&#xA;    @PageIndex INT = 1, --页数&#xD;&#xA;    @Count INT OUTPUT&#xD;&#xA;AS&#xD;&#xA;BEGIN&#xD;&#xA;    SELECT pd.Date,&#xD;&#xA;           Project.ID,&#xD;&#xA;           Number,&#xD;&#xA;           ProjectName,&#xD;&#xA;           CompanyName_PartyA,&#xD;&#xA;           CashAccounts.Salesman,&#xD;&#xA;           SalesDepartment,&#xD;&#xA;           ProductCategory,&#xD;&#xA;           Plans.Id PlanID,&#xD;&#xA;           pd.VehicleNo,&#xD;&#xA;           pd.VehicleNum,&#xD;&#xA;           Plans.Grade1,&#xD;&#xA;           Plans.Feature,&#xD;&#xA;           Plans.Quantity PlanQuantity,&#xD;&#xA;           pd.FaceQuantity,&#xD;&#xA;           ActQuantity,&#xD;&#xA;           pd.SignedQuantity,&#xD;&#xA;           pd.HaulDistance,&#xD;&#xA;           CashAccountUsedDetails.UsedAmount&#xD;&#xA;    INTO #TempDetails&#xD;&#xA;    FROM dbo.CashAccounts WITH (NOLOCK)&#xD;&#xA;        LEFT JOIN dbo.CashAccountProjects WITH (NOLOCK)&#xD;&#xA;            ON CashAccountID = CashAccounts.ID&#xD;&#xA;               AND CashAccountProjects.IsDeleted = 0&#xD;&#xA;        LEFT JOIN dbo.Project WITH (NOLOCK)&#xD;&#xA;            ON CashAccountProjects.ProjectID = Project.ID&#xD;&#xA;        LEFT JOIN dbo.CashAccountUsedDetails WITH (NOLOCK)&#xD;&#xA;            ON CashAccountUsedDetails.ProjectID = CashAccountProjects.ProjectID&#xD;&#xA;               AND CashAccountUsedDetails.IsDeleted = 0&#xD;&#xA;               AND BusinessType IN ( 0, 1 )&#xD;&#xA;        LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.ProductionDetails pd WITH (NOLOCK)&#xD;&#xA;            ON MesProductionDetailID = pd.Id&#xD;&#xA;        LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.Plans Plans WITH (NOLOCK)&#xD;&#xA;            ON pd.PlanId = Plans.Id&#xD;&#xA;    WHERE CashAccounts.IsDeleted = 0&#xD;&#xA;          AND CashAccounts.Salesman = ISNULL(@Salesman, CashAccounts.Salesman)&#xD;&#xA;          AND&#xD;&#xA;          (&#xD;&#xA;              CompanyName_PartyA LIKE '%' + ISNULL(@CompanyName, '') + '%'&#xD;&#xA;              OR ProjectName LIKE '%' + ISNULL(@ProjectName, '') + '%'&#xD;&#xA;          )&#xD;&#xA;          AND ProductCategory = ISNULL(@ProductCategory, ProductCategory)&#xD;&#xA;          AND Plans.Grade1 = ISNULL(@Grade, Plans.Grade1)&#xD;&#xA;    AND pd.Date&#xD;&#xA;    BETWEEN ISNULL(@StartDate, pd.Date) AND ISNULL(@EndData, GETDATE());&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;   " StatementId="1" StatementCompId="2" StatementType="SELECT INTO" RetrievedFromCache="true" StatementSubTreeCost="354.086" StatementEstRows="1" SELECT DISTINCT
           pr.SiteId,
           do.Material
    INTO #TempIpc
    FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.IpcProducts pr WITH (NOLOCK)
        INNER JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.IpcPieces pie WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON pie.ProductId = pr.Id
        INNER JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.IpcDosages do WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON do.PieceId = pie.Id
    WHERE pr.SiteProdTime BETWEEN @starttiem AND @endtime;

				MAX(CASE Material WHEN N'F135' THEN FactAmt ELSE 0 END ) AS 'F135',

				MAX(CASE Material WHEN N'F137' THEN FactAmt ELSE 0 END ) AS 'F137',
				MAX(CASE Material WHEN N'F138' THEN FactAmt ELSE 0 END ) AS 'F138',
				MAX(CASE Material WHEN N'F139' THEN FactAmt ELSE 0 END ) AS 'F139',
				MAX(CASE Material WHEN N'F140' THEN FactAmt ELSE 0 END ) AS 'F140'
        FROM
        (
            SELECT pd.SiteId,pd.[IpcProductId],
                   ISNULL(stm.ColumnName, pd.Material) AS Material,
                   SUM(pd.[RecipeAmt]) AS RecipeAmt,
                   SUM(pd.[PlanAmt]) AS PlanAmt,
                   SUM(pd.[FactAmt]) AS FactAmt
            FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.Vw_IpcNewProductDetails pd
                INNER JOIN dbo.Stations st ON st.isDeleted = 0 AND st.StationID_ProductionSys = pd.SiteId
	LEFT JOIN dbo.MaterialMapping mmMap ON mmMap.isDeleted = 0  AND st.id = mmMap.StationID AND pd.Material = mmMap.RecipeMtrName
	LEFT JOIN dbo.Materials stm ON stm.isDeleted = 0 AND stm.MaterialName = mmMap.CSEMtrName
            WHERE (
                      (
                          pd.SiteProdTime >=@ReportDate
                          AND pd.SiteProdTime < DATEADD(DAY, 1, @ReportDate)
                      )
                  )
            GROUP BY pd.SiteId,pd.[IpcProductId],
                     ISNULL(stm.ColumnName, pd.Material)
        ) p
        GROUP BY SiteId,IpcProductId
    ) pd
        ON p.SiteId=pd.SiteId and p.IpcProductId = pd.IpcProductId
GROUP BY p.SiteId,
         p.TerminalId,
         p.TerminalName,
         p.ProjectId,
         p.StProjectId,
         p.ProjectName,
         p.BuilderName,
         p.ConcreteCategory,
         p.Position,
         p.Grade;

INSERT  INTO dbo.SalesProjectMaterialUsageCostDetails
            ( FGC_CreateDate ,
              FGC_LastModifier ,
              FGC_LastModifyDate ,
              FGC_Creator ,
              SalesProjectPriceDiffMonthID ,
              MaterialID ,
              MaterialName ,
              FactQty ,
              AvgUPrice ,
              TotalAmt
			 )
            SELECT  GETDATE() ,
                    @Operator ,
                    GETDATE() ,
                    @Operator ,
                    SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.ID ,
                    MaterialID ,
                    MaterialName ,
                    SUM(FactAmt) ,
                    ISNULL(AvgUPrice, 0) ,
                    SUM(ISNULL(FactAmt, 0) / 1000 * ISNULL(AvgUPrice, 0))
            FROM    #TempProduct
                    INNER JOIN #TempDetails ON #TempProduct.ProductionDetailId = #TempDetails.OriginalID
                    INNER JOIN SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth ON SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.PeriodID = @PeriodID
                                                             AND SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.StationID = #TempDetails.StationID
                                                             AND SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.ProjectID = #TempDetails.ProjectID
                                                             AND SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.ProjectName = #TempDetails.ProjectName
                                                             AND SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.Customer = #TempDetails.Customer
                                                             AND SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.Grade = #TempDetails.Grade
                                                             AND SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.IsProvidePump = #TempDetails.IsProvidePump
            GROUP BY SalesProjectPriceDiffMonth.ID ,
                    MaterialID ,
                    MaterialName ,
                    ISNULL(AvgUPrice, 0);

UPDATE ins
	   SET ReceivingDailyReportID = r.ID
	   FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		   left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		   left JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON ins.TenantId = r.TenantID
				  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	   WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			 AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
			 AND r.ID = ISNULL(@ReportID, r.ID);

SELECT *
    INTO #TempData
    FROM
    (
        SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY SourceId ORDER BY np.LastModificationTime DESC) Num,
               Stations.ID StationID,
               SourceId ProjectID,
               d.Distance
        FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.NProjects np
            LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.SiteNProjectDistances d WITH (NOLOCK)
                ON d.TenantId = np.TenantId
                   AND d.ProjectId = np.Id
            LEFT JOIN dbo.Stations WITH (NOLOCK)
                ON StationID_ProductionSys = d.Id
        WHERE np.TenantId = @TenantID
              AND np.IsDeleted = 0
              AND NOT EXISTS
        (
            SELECT 1
            FROM dbo.ProjectDistance WITH (NOLOCK)
            WHERE StationID = Stations.ID
                  AND ProjectID = np.SourceId
        )
    ) insertData
    WHERE insertData.Num = 1;

INSERT INTO dbo.ProductionDailyReportDetails
    (
        FGC_CreateDate,
        FGC_LastModifier,
        FGC_LastModifyDate,
        FGC_Creator,
        DailyReportID,
        Type,
        OriginalID,
        OriginalProjectID,
        OriginalPlanID,
        ProjectName,
        Customer,
        SalesDepartment,
        Salesman,
        PaymentType,
        ProductCategory,
        Unit,
        ConstructionPosition,
        StrengthGrade,
        Discharge,
        ReceiptDate,
        ProductionLine,
        ProductionTime,
        VehicleNum,
        VehicleSequence,
        Driver,
        PlanType,
        ApplicationUser,
        ProductionCoefficient,
        ProductionQty_M3,
        ProductionQty_T,
        ReceiptQty,
        SignedQty_M3,
        SignedQty_T,
        FinalQty_M3,
        FinalQty_T,
        TSFInQty,
        TSFOutQty,
        ActualSupplyQty_M3,
        ActualSupplyQty_T,
        SignCopy,
        Distance,
        Overtime,
        ProductionRemarks,
        LogisticsCoefficient,
        LogisticsFinalQty_M3,
        ProjectID,
        SalesCoefficient,
		SalesRemarks,
        LogisticsOvertime,
        SlumpTypes,
        VehicleRegNum,
        Grade1,
        Feature,
        IsProvidePump,
        IfManualUpdated,
        AcumltQuantity,
        SignedQtyDiffReasonType,
        Area,
        TechnologyRequest,
		StubCopy,
		ShipmentCount,
		Paid,
		ScaleDiff,
		LossQty,
		PrintTime,
		PrintOperatorID,
		PrintOperator,
		Metre,
		OtherPumpType,
		ProductionPlanNumber,
		PlatformCustomer,
		PlatformCustomerPhone,
		EGCBOrderID
    )
    SELECT
        FGC_CreateDate=GETDATE(),
        FGC_LastModifier=@Creator ,
        FGC_LastModifyDate=GETDATE() ,
        FGC_Creator=@Creator ,
        DailyReportID = r.ID,
        Type = ISNULL(ISNULL(mt.ProductionNature,Stations.Type),'自产'),
        OriginalID = mt.Id,
        OriginalProjectID = mt.ProjectId,
        OriginalPlanID = mt.PlanId,
        ProjectName = mt.ProjectName,
        Customer = mt.CompanyName,
        SalesDepartment =ISNULL(mt.Department, @DefaultDepartment),
        Salesman =  ISNULL(mt.PersonInCharge, '未填'),
        PaymentType = ISNULL(mt.PaymentType, @DefaultPaymentType),
        ProductCategory =ISNULL(mt.ConcreteCategory, @DefaultProductCategory) ,
		Unit = ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit),
		ConstructionPosition = mt.Position,
		StrengthGrade = mt.Grade,
		Discharge = mt.DischargeType,
		ReceiptDate = CAST(mt.Date AS DATE),
		ProductionLine = mt.TerminalNo,
		ProductionTime = mt.ProductionTime,
		VehicleNum = mt.VehicleNo,
		VehicleSequence=mt.VehicleNum,
		Driver = mt.DriverName,
		PlanType = mt.Type,
		ApplicationUser = mt.Creator,
		ProductionCoefficient = CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END,
		ProductionQty_M3 = CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN
										mt.ActQuantity / (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
								ELSE mt.ActQuantity END,--生产方量=如果单位=吨，就取【mt.ActQuantity/生产容重系数】，否则=【mt.ActQuantity】
		ProductionQty_T = CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN mt.ActQuantity ELSE NULL END,--生产吨量=如果单位=吨，就取【mt.ActQuantity】，否则=【null】
		ReceiptQty = mt.FaceQuantity,
		SignedQty_M3 = CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
								(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
							ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END) END,--签收方量=如果单位=吨，就取【实际签收量/容重】
		SignedQty_T=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
					(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
					ELSE NULL END,--签收吨量=如果单位=吨，就取【实际签收量】
		FinalQty_M3=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '方' THEN 
						(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
						ELSE NULL END,--销售方量=如果单位=方，就取【实际签收量】
		FinalQty_T=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
					(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
					ELSE NULL END,--销售吨量=如果单位=吨，就取【实际签收量】
		TSFInQty=mt.TransferIn,
		TSFOutQty=mt.TransferOut,
		ActualSupplyQty_M3=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
									(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN  (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN mt.ActQuantity ELSE NULL END)+mt.TransferIn-mt.TransferOut ELSE NULL END)
									/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
								ELSE 
									(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN mt.ActQuantity / (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END) ELSE mt.ActQuantity END)+mt.TransferIn-mt.TransferOut
								END,--实供方量=如果单位=吨，就取【实供吨量/生产容重系数】，否则=【生产方量+调入-调出】
		ActualSupplyQty_T=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
								(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN mt.ActQuantity ELSE NULL END)+mt.TransferIn-mt.TransferOut
							ELSE NULL END,--实供吨量=如果单位=吨，就取【生产吨量+调入-调出】
		SignCopy=mt.ReceiptSigned,
		Distance=CASE WHEN mt.DeliveryDistance>0 THEN mt.DeliveryDistance ELSE mt.HaulDistance END,--运距=如果签收运距>0 取【签收运距】，否则取【计划运距】
		Overtime = mt.Overtime,
		ProductionRemarks='更新日志：'+ISNULL(mt.UpdateLogs,'')+'；报表备注：'+ ISNULL(mt.Comment,'') +'；小票备注：'+ ISNULL(mt.PrintComment,''),--生产备注
		LogisticsCoefficient=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END,--物流容重系数=生产容重系数
		LogisticsFinalQty_M3=CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
									(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
								ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END) END,--物流方量=签收方量
		ProjectID=mt.SourceId1,
		SalesCoefficient= CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END,--销售容重=生产容重系数
		SalesRemarks=mt.Remark,--销售备注
		LogisticsOvertime=mt.Overtime,
		SlumpTypes=mt.Slump,
		VehicleRegNum=mt.VehiclePlate,
		Grade1=mt.Grade1,
		Feature=CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.Feature,'')='' THEN NULL ELSE mt.Feature END,
		IsProvidePump=mt.IsProvidePump,
		0 IfManualUpdated,
		AcumltQuantity=mt.AcumltQuantity,
		SignedQtyDiffReasonType=mt.SignedQtyDiffReason,
		Area=mt.Region,
		TechnologyRequest=TechnologyRequest,
		StubCopy=1,
		ShipmentCount=1,
		Paid=0,
		ScaleDiff=CASE WHEN mt.SignedQtyDiffReason=2 THEN 
					mt.FaceQuantity-
					(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
							(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
							(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
							ELSE NULL END)
					 ELSE 
					        (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
								(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
							ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END) END)
					 END)
		          ELSE 
				    NULL
				  END,--磅差=如果SignedQtyDiffReasonType=2，则取【如果单位=吨，就用票面量-签收吨量，否则用票面量-签收方量】，否则=null
		LossQty=CASE WHEN mt.SignedQtyDiffReason IN (3,4,5) THEN 
		             mt.FaceQuantity-
					(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
							(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
							(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)
							ELSE NULL END)
					 ELSE 
					        (CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN 
								(CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END)/(CASE WHEN ISNULL(pc.Unit, @DefaultUnit) = '吨' THEN @ProCoeff ELSE NULL END)
							ELSE (CASE WHEN ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(mt.SignedQuantity, mt.FaceQuantity) END) END)
					 END)
				ELSE 
				    NULL
				END,--损耗=如果签收方量差异在345 则（如果单位=吨  就用）
		mt.PrintTime,
		mt.PrintOperatorID,
		mt.PrintOperator,
		Metre=mt.Meters,
		OtherPumpType=mt.OtherPumpType,
		mt.Code,
		mt.EgcbOrderCreator,
		mt.EgcbOrderCreatorPhone,
		mt.EGCBOrderID
    FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.[ProductDetailsDino-mt] mt WITH (NOLOCK)
		--[172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.[ProductDetailsDino-mt] mt WITH (NOLOCK)
        INNER JOIN dbo.Stations WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON Stations.StationID_ProductionSys = mt.SiteId AND Stations.isDeleted=0
        INNER JOIN ProductionDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON r.StationID = Stations.ID
               AND r.isDeleted = 0
               AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
        LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductCategories pc WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON pc.CategoryName = ISNULL(mt.ConcreteCategory, @DefaultProductCategory)
    WHERE mt.TenantId=@TenantID AND
		  mt.SiteDate >= @ReportDate
          AND mt.SiteDate < DATEADD(DAY, 1, @ReportDate) --生成17号日报  获取>=17 0:00  <18 0:00的数据
	UNION
	SELECT FGC_CreateDate = GETDATE(),
		FGC_LastModifier = @Creator,
		FGC_LastModifyDate = GETDATE(),
		FGC_Creator =@Creator,
		DailyReportID = r.ID,
		Type = Stations.Type,
		OriginalID=RIGHT(Shipping.Number,12),
		OriginalProjectID,
		OriginalPlanID=NULL,
		ProjectName=Shipping.ProjectName,
		Customer=Shipping.Consignee,
		SalesDepartment=ISNULL(Project.SalesDepartment, @DefaultDepartment),
		Salesman=ISNULL(Project.Salesman,'未填'),
		PaymentType=ISNULL(Project.SalesPaymentType,@DefaultPaymentType),
		ProductCategory=ISNULL(up.ConcreteCategory,'干混砂浆'),
		Unit=@DefaultGHSJUnit,
		ConstructionPosition=Shipping.Position,
		StrengthGrade=ISNULL(Delivering.grade,Delivering.Item+'-'+Delivering.Specification),
		Discharge=NULL,
		ReceiptDate = CAST(Delivering.GrossTime AS DATE),
		ProductionLine=NULL,
		ProductionTime=Delivering.GrossTime,
		VehicleNum=Delivering.Vehicle,
		VehicleSequence=NULL,
		Driver=NULL,
		PlanType=up.Type,
		ApplicationUser=up.Creator,
		ProductionCoefficient=NULL,
		ProductionQty_M3=NULL,
		ProductionQty_T=Delivering.RealNet/1000,
		ReceiptQty=Delivering.Net/1000,
		SignedQty_M3=NULL,
		SignedQty_T=Delivering.Net/1000,
		FinalQty_M3=NULL,
		FinalQty_T=Delivering.Net/1000,
		TSFInQty=NULL,
		TSFOutQty=NULL,
		ActualSupplyQty_M3=NULL,
		ActualSupplyQty_T=Delivering.Net/1000,
		SignCopy=NULL,
		Distance=p.HaulDistance,
		Overtime=NULL,
		ProductionRemarks=NULL,
		LogisticsCoefficient=NULL,
		LogisticsFinalQty_M3=NULL,
		ProjectID=Shipping.ProjectID,
		SalesCoefficient=NULL,
		SalesRemarks=NULL,
		LogisticsOvertime=NULL,
		SlumpTypes=NULL,
		VehicleRegNum=NULL,
		grade1=Delivering.grade1,
		feature=CASE WHEN ISNULL(Delivering.feature,'')='' THEN NULL ELSE Delivering.feature END,
		IsProvidePump=NULL,
		IfManualUpdated=0,
		AcumltQuantity=NULL,
		SignedQtyDiffReasonType=NULL,
		Area=NULL,
		TechnologyRequest=NULL,
		StubCopy=1,
		ShipmentCount=NULL,
		Paid=0,
		ScaleDiff=NULL,
		LossQty=NULL,
		PrintTime=NULL,
		PrintOperatorID=NULL,
		PrintOperator=NULL,
		Metre=NULL,
		OtherPumpType=NULL,
		p.Code,
		up.EgcbOrderCreator,
	    up.EgcbOrderCreatorPhone,
		up.EGCBOrderID
	FROM 
	[Weighbridge-SG].dbo.Shipping Shipping WITH (NOLOCK)
	LEFT JOIN [Weighbridge-SG].dbo.Delivering Delivering WITH (NOLOCK)
		ON Shipping.DeliveringID = Delivering.ID
	LEFT JOIN  [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.UserPlans up WITH(NOLOCK) ON Delivering.UserPlanID=up.id
	LEFT JOIN  [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.Plans p WITH(NOLOCK) ON up.PlanId=p.id
	--[Weighbridge-SG].dbo.Shipping Shipping WITH (NOLOCK)
	--LEFT JOIN [Weighbridge-SG].dbo.Delivering Delivering WITH (NOLOCK)
	--	ON Shipping.DeliveringID = Delivering.ID
	LEFT JOIN dbo.Project WITH(NOLOCK) ON Shipping.ProjectID=Project.ID
	INNER JOIN dbo.Stations WITH (NOLOCK)
		ON Stations.StationID_WeighbridgeSys = Shipping.StationID
			AND Stations.isDeleted = 0
	INNER JOIN ProductionDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		ON r.StationID = Stations.ID
			AND r.isDeleted = 0
			AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
	WHERE Shipping.isDeleted = 0
		AND Delivering.GrossTime >=DATEADD(HOUR,@DefaultFinancialTime,@ReportDate)
		AND Delivering.GrossTime < DATEADD(DAY, 1, DATEADD(HOUR,@DefaultFinancialTime,@ReportDate)) --生成17号日报  获取>=17 0:00  <18 0:00的数据
		AND Shipping.isDeleted=0 AND Delivering.isDeleted=0

UPDATE ins
	   SET ReceivingDailyReportID = r.ID
	   FROM dbo.ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		   left JOIN dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails d WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON r.ID = d.DailyReportID
		   left JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns ins WITH (NOLOCK)
			   ON ins.TenantId = r.TenantID
				  AND d.OriginalID = ins.Id
	   WHERE r.isDeleted = 0
			 AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
			 AND r.ID = ISNULL(@ReportID, r.ID);

INSERT INTO dbo.ReceivingDailyReportDetails
    (
        FGC_CreateDate,
        FGC_LastModifier,
        FGC_LastModifyDate,
        FGC_Creator,
        DailyReportID,
        OriginalID,
        VendorID,
        OriginalVendor,
        MaterialID,
        Material,
        Specification,
        RealGross,
        RealTare,
        RealNet,
        Gross,
        Tare,
        Net,
        VendorNet,
        Coefficient,
        SettlementQty,
        NetUCost,
        NetAmt,
        TaxRate,
        TaxUCost,
        TaxAmt,
        SetmtIncdTax,
        SettlementAmt,
        TransportationCharge,
        WithholdingTaxAmt,
        VehicleNum,
        ReceivingOperator,
        ReceivingTime,
        ReceivingNum,
        Warehouse,
        Remarks,
        StatementID,
        VendorCode,
        ItemCode,
        Manufacturer,
        CurrentInvoiceCorpName,
        VendorNum,
        VendorTime,
        AgentReceivingID,
        TransportationQty,
        TransportationUCost,
        TransportationVenndorID,
        PlatformPrice,
        AccountingPrice,
        PlatformAmt,
        AccountingAmt,
        TransStatementID,
        CompanyID,
        TareTime,
        CashPrice,
        CashAmt,
        VendorsTypeSetID,
		ActualMoistureRate,
		MESCreateFrom,
		MESReason,
		LighteringQty,
		LighteringVenndorID
    )
	SELECT
        FGC_CreateDate=GETDATE(),
        FGC_LastModifier=@Creator,
        FGC_LastModifyDate=GETDATE(),
        FGC_Creator=@Creator,
        DailyReportID=r.ID,
        OriginalID=Ins.Id,
        VendorID=Vendors.ID,
        OriginalVendor=Ins.VendorName,
        MaterialID=Ins.MaterialID,
        Material=ISNULL(Ins.ItemName,Ins.MaterialName),
        Specification=Ins.Specification,
        RealGross=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.GrossWeightActual,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.GrossWeightActual,0) END,
        RealTare=NULL,
        RealNet=NULL,
        Gross=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.GrossWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.GrossWeight,0) END,
        Tare=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.TareWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.TareWeight,0) END,
        Net=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0) END,
        VendorNet=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0) END,
        Coefficient=@ProCoeff,
        SettlementQty=CASE WHEN @IsMinQty=1 THEN 
		                   (CASE WHEN ROUND((CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0) END),CASE WHEN @IsRound1=1 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END)<ROUND((CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0) END),CASE WHEN @IsRound1=1 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END)
						         THEN ROUND((CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0) END),CASE WHEN @IsRound1=1 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END)
								 ELSE ROUND((CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0) END),CASE WHEN @IsRound1=1 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END)
						    END)
					  ELSE 
						   ROUND((CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN 
									 (CASE WHEN vendors.SettlementQtyMethod=1 THEN ISNULL(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0) ELSE ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0) END)/1000 
							     ELSE (CASE WHEN vendors.SettlementQtyMethod=1 THEN ISNULL(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0) ELSE ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0) END) 
								 END)
								 ,CASE WHEN @IsRound1=1 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END)
					  END,--IF(MinQty="Y",MIN(Net,VendorNet),Net)
        NetUCost=NULL,
        NetAmt=NULL,
        TaxRate=NULL,
        TaxUCost=NULL,
        TaxAmt=NULL,
        SetmtIncdTax=1,
        SettlementAmt=NULL,
        TransportationCharge=0.00,
        WithholdingTaxAmt=NULL,
        VehicleNum=Ins.VendorCar,
        ReceivingOperator=Ins.MiEmployeeName,
        ReceivingTime=CASE WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=0 THEN MiDate WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=1 THEN GrossWeightTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=2 THEN TareWeightTime END,
        ReceivingNum=Ins.MiSerial,
        Warehouse=Ins.Warehouse,
        Remarks=Ins.Remark,
        StatementID=NULL,
        VendorCode=Ins.VendorCode,
        ItemCode=Ins.ItemCode,
        Manufacturer=Ins.Manufacturer,
        CurrentInvoiceCorpName=Ins.CurrentInvoiceCorpName,
        VendorNum=Ins.VendorSerial,
        VendorTime=Ins.VendorTime,
        AgentReceivingID=NULL,
        TransportationQty=ROUND((CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0) END),CASE WHEN @IsRound1=1 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END),
        TransportationUCost=NULL,
        TransportationVenndorID=Vendors.MaterialTransportationVendorID,
        PlatformPrice=NULL,
        AccountingPrice=NULL,
        PlatformAmt=NULL,
        AccountingAmt=NULL,
        TransStatementID=NULL,
        CompanyID=Ins.CompanyID,
        TareTime=NULL,
        CashPrice=NULL,
        CashAmt=0.00,
        VendorsTypeSetID=Vendors.VendorsTypeSetID,
		ActualMoistureRate=Ins.ActualMoistureRate,
		Ins.CreatFrom,
		Ins.Reason,
		LighteringQty=ROUND((CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE ISNULL(Ins.NetWeight,0) END),CASE WHEN @IsRound1=1 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END),
		LighteringVenndorID=Vendors.MaterialLighteringVenndorID
    FROM [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.WbMaterialIns Ins WITH (NOLOCK)
        INNER JOIN dbo.Stations WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON Stations.StationID_PurchaseSys = Ins.SiteId AND Stations.isDeleted=0
        INNER JOIN ReceivingDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
            ON r.StationID = Stations.ID
               AND r.isDeleted = 0
               AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Vendors WITH(NOLOCK) ON Ins.VendorCode=Vendors.VendorCode AND Vendors.isDeleted=0
    WHERE Ins.TenantId=@TenantID 
		  AND Ins.ReceivingDailyReportID IS NULL  
		  AND(CASE WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=0 THEN MiDate WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=1 THEN GrossWeightTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=2 THEN TareWeightTime END) >= DATEADD(HOUR,@DefaultFinancialTime,@ReportDate)
          AND (CASE WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=0 THEN MiDate WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=1 THEN GrossWeightTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=2 THEN TareWeightTime END) < DATEADD(DAY, 1, DATEADD(HOUR,@DefaultFinancialTime,@ReportDate)) --生成17号日报  获取>=17 0:00  <18 0:00的数据
		  AND Ins.IsDeleted=0

        OriginalID=rec.ID,--111
        --VendorID=Vendors.ID,

        RealTare=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN rec.RealTare/1000 ELSE rec.RealTare END,
        RealNet=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN rec.RealNet/1000 ELSE rec.RealNet END,
        Gross=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN rec.Gross/1000 ELSE rec.Gross END,--111
        Tare=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN rec.Tare/1000 ELSE rec.Tare END,--111
        Net=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN rec.Net/1000 ELSE rec.Net END,--111
        --VendorNet=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN isnull(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE isnull(Ins.VendorNetWeight,0) END,
        Coefficient=rec.Coefficient,
        SettlementQty=CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN rec.AccountingNet/1000 ELSE rec.AccountingNet END,
        NetUCost=NULL,

        ReceivingTime=(CASE WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=0 THEN rec.StartTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=1 THEN GrossTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=2 THEN TareTime END),--111
        ReceivingNum=rec.Number,--111
        Warehouse=rec.Warehouse,
        Remarks=NULL,
        StatementID=NULL,
        --VendorCode=Ins.VendorCode,
        --ItemCode=Ins.ItemCode,
        --Manufacturer=Ins.Manufacturer,
        --CurrentInvoiceCorpName=Ins.CurrentInvoiceCorpName,
        --VendorNum=Ins.VendorSerial,
        --VendorTime=Ins.VendorTime,
        AgentReceivingID=NULL,
        --TransportationQty=ROUND((CASE WHEN @DefaultUnit=0 THEN isnull(Ins.NetWeight,0)/1000 ELSE isnull(Ins.NetWeight,0) END),CASE WHEN @IsRound1=1 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END),
        TransportationUCost=NULL,
        --TransportationVenndorID=Vendors.MaterialTransportationVendorID,
        PlatformPrice=NULL,
        AccountingPrice=NULL,
        PlatformAmt=NULL,
        AccountingAmt=NULL,
        TransStatementID=NULL,
        --CompanyID=Ins.CompanyID,
        TareTime=NULL,
        CashPrice=NULL,
        CashAmt=NULL,
        --VendorsTypeSetID=Vendors.VendorsTypeSetID
	FROM 
	[WeighbridgeTest20230406].dbo.Receiving rec WITH(NOLOCK) 
	INNER JOIN dbo.Stations WITH (NOLOCK)
		ON Stations.StationID_WeighbridgeSys = rec.StationID
			AND Stations.isDeleted = 0
	INNER JOIN ProductionDailyReports r WITH (NOLOCK)
		ON r.StationID = Stations.ID
			AND r.isDeleted = 0
			AND r.ReportDate = @ReportDate
	WHERE rec.isDeleted = 0
		AND (CASE WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=0 THEN rec.StartTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=1 THEN GrossTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=2 THEN TareTime END) >=@ReportDate
		AND (CASE WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=0 THEN rec.StartTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=1 THEN GrossTime WHEN @DefaultRecvTimeType=2 THEN TareTime END) < DATEADD(DAY, 1, @ReportDate) --生成17号日报  获取>=17 0:00  <18 0:00的数据
		AND Stations.IsHaveIPC=0

SELECT  Details.ID,
			Details.OriginalID ,
			Details.Type,
            Reports.StationID ,
            Details.ProjectID ,
            CASE WHEN Project.Type = 0
                      OR ( Project.Type = 1
                           AND Project.AgentID IS NOT NULL
                         ) THEN Details.ProjectName
                 ELSE Project.ProjectName
            END ProjectName ,--如果是现金/代理商才根据工程核算账户、工程名称、施工单位分组
            CASE WHEN Project.Type = 0
                      OR ( Project.Type = 1
                           AND Project.AgentID IS NOT NULL
                         ) THEN Details.Customer
                 ELSE Project.CompanyName_PartyA
            END Customer ,
            Details.StrengthGrade Grade ,
            ISNULL(CASE WHEN ProductCategories.Unit = '吨' THEN Details.FinalQty_T ELSE Details.FinalQty_M3 END, 0)FinalQty,
			ISNULL(CASE WHEN ProductCategories.Unit = '吨' THEN Details.ProductionQty_T ELSE Details.ProductionQty_M3 END, 0)ProductionQty,
            Details.IsProvidePump ,
			ProductCategories.Unit,
			ISNULL(Details.SalesTotalAmt1,0)ReportSalesTotalAmt,
			 --下面是提供给奥润使用
			 Details.RelatedStationID,
			 Details.OriginalProductCategory,
			 Details.OriginalStrengthGrade
    INTO    #TempDetails
    FROM    dbo.ProductionDailyReports Reports WITH ( NOLOCK )
            INNER JOIN ProductionDailyReportDetails Details WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON Reports.ID = Details.DailyReportID
            INNER JOIN dbo.Project WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON Details.ProjectID = Project.ID
            INNER JOIN dbo.ProductCategories WITH ( NOLOCK ) ON Project.ProductCategory = ProductCategories.CategoryName
    WHERE   CONVERT(VARCHAR(100), Reports.ReportDate, 23) BETWEEN @StartDate
                                                          AND @EndDate
            AND ISNULL(Reports.isDeleted, 0) = 0
            AND Details.ProjectID IS NOT NULL;

SELECT ID = detail.ID,                                    --日报明细ID
		   ProjectType=SalesPaymentType.Type,
		   AccountingPaymentType=ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, ''),
		--这里主要是为了区分  每一条明细使用的价格类型是什么  核算账户价格、代理商价格、现金销售政策价格
		  CalcType = CASE  
					 WHEN @BusinessType='SalesPriceCalculatePrice' THEN 
							CASE WHEN ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') != '现金' AND AutoPricingSet.SettlementPriceMode != 2 THEN 1
								 WHEN  ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') = '现金' OR ( ISNULL(AccountingPaymentType, '') IN ('抵款','站点抵款') AND AutoPricingSet.SettlementPriceMode = 2 ) THEN 3 
							END
		             WHEN @BusinessType='AgentPriceCalculatePrice'AND ISNULL(AgentPriceDiff,0)=1 AND ISNULL(SalesDepartments.IsStationDepartment,0)=0 THEN 2 END,
					 --计算类型，销售日报自动挂价只区分合同价格和现金价格，给所有数据的合同金额字段、代理商金额字段挂价；代理商销售日报挂价，给有价差的代理商数据的代理商金额字段挂价
		   StationID = Report.StationID,
		   ProjectID = detail.ProjectID,                      --核算账户ID
		   AgentID = Project.AgentID,
		   ProductCategory = Project.ProductCategory,
		   IsBulkAndBagsSeparatePricing,                      --干混砂浆袋装混装是否单独计价
		   AutoPricingSet.CashUQtyAddPrice,
		   Unit = pc.Unit,
		   PlanId = MES.PlanId,                               --生产计划
		   ReportID = Report.ID,
		   ReportDate = Report.ReportDate,                    --报表日期
		   PeriodID = Periods.ID,                             --账期ID
		   SalesUnitWeigh = Project.SalesUnitWeigh,
		   StrengthGrade = detail.StrengthGrade,              --标准标号
		   Grade1 = detail.Grade1,                            --纯标号
		   Feature = detail.Feature,                          --性能拼接字段
		   FinalQty_T = detail.FinalQty_T,                    --销售吨量
		   FinalQty_M3 = detail.FinalQty_M3,                  --销售方量
		   Discharge = detail.Discharge,                      --卸料方式,
		   IsLubricatePumpMortar = MES.IsLubricatePumpMortar, --是否润泵砂浆
		   OriginalPlanGrade1 = MES.OriginalPlanGrade1,       --润泵砂浆关联原计划标号
		   OriginalPlanFeature = MES.OriginalPlanFeature,     --润泵砂浆关联原计划特殊要求
		   Overtime,                                          --超时时长
		   Distance = detail.Distance,                        --运距
		   VehicleNum = detail.VehicleSequence,
		   detail.IsProvidePump,--是否我方提供泵
		   detail.OtherPumpType--其他泵型
	INTO #TempData
	FROM ProductionDailyReportDetails detail WITH (NOLOCK)
		LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductionDailyReports Report WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.DailyReportID = Report.ID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.SalesDepartments WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.SalesDepartment = DepartmentName AND SalesDepartments.isDeleted = 0
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Project WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.ProjectID = Project.ID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.ProductCategories pc WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.ProductCategory = pc.CategoryName
		LEFT JOIN [172.16.199.200].[logistics-mt-prod].dbo.View_GetProductionDetailsAndLPM MES WITH (NOLOCK) ON detail.OriginalID = MES.Id
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Periods WITH (NOLOCK) ON Report.ReportDate BETWEEN Periods.StartDate AND EndDate AND ISNULL(Periods.isDeleted, 0) = 0
		LEFT JOIN dbo.AutoPricingSet WITH (NOLOCK) ON BusinessType = 'Project' AND BusinessRelationID = detail.ProjectID AND AutoPricingSet.ProjectID = detail.ProjectID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.SalesPaymentType WITH(NOLOCK) ON Project.AccountingPaymentType=SalesPaymentType.PaymentType 
	WHERE ISNULL(Report.isDeleted, 0) = 0
		  AND detail.ProjectID IS NOT NULL
		  AND ISNULL(detail.IfManualUpdated, 0) = 0
		  AND Report.ReportDate
		  BETWEEN @StartDate AND @EndDate
		  AND ISNULL(detail.StrengthGrade, '') != ''
		  AND detail.TYPE IN (SELECT col FROM dbo.f_split((SELECT ParaValue FROM dbo.Parameters WHERE ParaName='ProjectSalesTypeFilter'),','))
		  AND ISNULL(SalesUPrice1,0)=0;
